data.description: Welcome to this charming single-level home nestled on a spacious corner lot, offering both comfort & convenience. Primely located near a diverse selection of restaurants, shopping & entertainment + minutes from freeway access. As you step inside you'll be greeted by an open & airy layout that seamlessly combines the living, dining & kitchen areas. The darling corner brick gas fireplace adds a touch of character and warmth, making it an inviting space to unwind. Kitchen features an eat-in breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances (New '19) + refrigerator included! Enjoy an additional large family room or bonus/rec room perfect for a variety of needs. Three bedrooms offer comfort and tranquility, with the primary bedroom featuring an en-suite bathroom for added privacy. Walk-in shower redone by Dreamstyle Remodeling + new carpet & vinyl in primary (May '23). Fully fenced backyard complete with full automatic sprinklers. Exterior of home & gutters painted & gutter guards installed in '20. It's time to come home!
